name: Insurance Fraugg
description:
This game was made as a part of Forsberg Gamejam 2020, January by:

Isac Selander, Elliot Holmqvist, Axel Marelius, Edward Sedelius, Nicholas Harris and Max Roberts (https://maxrobertstudios.itch.io/).

CONTROLS

Press A to launch character. Try to get as damaged as possible.
